original_title: City Hall to Harlem in 15 Seconds, Via the Subway Route
overview: Casey entering subway at City Hall Station and goes in the tunnel. Casey lights a fuse to set off a blast and running away. Thinking the fuse has gone out, he creeps cautiously up to it, when it suddenly goes off, blowing Casey through the tunnel.
title: City Hall to Harlem in 15 Seconds, Via the Subway Route
